Tree wide: Unify initialization of multi-value value lists.

Use struct initializers to initialize the array like so:

  value_t values[] = {
    /* ... */
  };

Then initialize the value_list_t with:

  vl.values = values;
  vl.values_len = STATIC_ARRAY_SIZE (values);

